emuInput.TitMainTitle: Groom Wayne Leonard Carroll and bride Rose Ann Simpkins Carroll wearing gown with lace sleeves, posed behind three tiered cake in Greene Hearth
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 23, 1965, pg. 6 reads: "Newlyweds - Mr. and Mrs. Wayne Leonard Carroll were recently married in Sixth Mt. Zion Baptist Church. The bride is the former Rose Ann Simpkins, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Ellis J. Simpkins of Penn Hills -Harris Photo."
